# ğŸŒ Country Flag Designs using HTML & CSS

## ğŸ“Œ Project Overview

This project showcases the design of various **country flags** using **HTML** and **CSS**. The main focus of the project is to demonstrate the understanding and practical implementation of the **CSS Box Model** and **Basic Cascading concepts**.

Each flag is created using simple HTML elements and styled using CSS properties such as margins, padding, borders, width, height, colors, and positioning.

---

## ğŸ¯ Objectives

* Practice and understand the **CSS Box Model**
* Learn **CSS Cascading and Styling Priority**
* Improve layout designing skills using pure CSS
* Strengthen front-end fundamentals without using external libraries

